{"tid":497024,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【英超】前曼聯領隊雲高爾：摩連奴踢法更沉悶","createTime":"2017-12-12T10:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T11:59:27.000Z","uid":161311,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb4a8e54e818d43e1f531d7bd3c631a6fb2ccd5","tid":497024,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/體育/140601/-英超-前曼聯領隊雲高爾-摩連奴踢法更沉悶\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F140601%2F-%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85-%E5%89%8D%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF%E9%A0%98%E9%9A%8A%E9%9B%B2%E9%AB%98%E7%88%BE-%E6%91%A9%E9%80%A3%E5%A5%B4%E8%B8%A2%E6%B3%95%E6%9B%B4%E6%B2%89%E6%82%B6&d=h2izqYTFbS8OV0hfSYxxT5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=36a81016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/體育/140601/-英超-前曼聯領隊雲高爾-摩連奴踢法更沉悶</a><br />\n<br />\n前曼聯領隊雲高爾表示，現時摩連奴帶領的曼聯，足球風格比他掌帥印時更加沉悶，他現時更喜歡看曼城的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n雲高爾談到贏得英格蘭足總盃後被炒的感受，他表示與接任的摩連奴關係良好，但他不滿曼聯執行副總裁艾活禾特不肯開誠布公。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯上周六於英超的曼市打吡戰中不敵曼城，雖續排次席，但落後榜首曼城的差距被拉開至11分。在2014年至2016年執教曼聯的雲高爾近日接受英國傳媒訪問，他認為曼城不但比曼聯強，踢出來的足球也更好看，「我喜歡看曼城的比賽多於曼聯的，你需要一套更有實力的陣容，而明顯地曼城的陣容更強。」<br />\n<br />\n在雲高爾執教的兩個球季，他為曼聯贏過英格蘭足總盃。他的足球理念十分重視控球，但當時曼聯常常在中後場傳球，被球迷批評踢悶蛋足球。不過，雲高爾認為現在的曼聯踢法更沉悶，「如果你要我評價在曼聯的工作，我會說，在這種工作環境之下，我度過了最好的時光。我們當時的踢法是正確，但在英格蘭不受青睞。」"},{"pid":"a09b053623f007aa1a0dd7e1be25083f614f7675","tid":497024,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"好撚串喎雲高爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b69addbe6781de97acc1e895963b24b0355e1e","tid":497024,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"v92<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a04fd3753242e81b2edf4b485822ba29b867ea","tid":497024,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚串喎雲高爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識攻唔識入呢<br />\n入球少到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd82735314b36522fc9ea8b4fdefd09c29fa0a46","tid":497024,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>v92<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0182fdb7c76fabab4bed0d5e579a755d8b34ccbe","tid":497024,"uid":47904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我個陣睇十場真係8場訓著"},{"pid":"4b688aec3f2636fc7646be1beee616454c7c6f42","tid":497024,"uid":12280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我個陣睇十場真係8場訓著</blockquote><br />\n10場有10場瞓著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35e55eb0b02ae3e69addc43c1926bfd84b062cc","tid":497024,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:59:27.000Z","msg":"前任獌領隊打今日獌領隊<br />\n<br />\n獌狗諗住保邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}